"powershell.exe" & {$folderarray = @(\""Desktop\"", \""Downloads\"", \""Documents\"", \""AppData/Local\"", \""AppData/Roaming\""), Get-ChildItem -Path $env:homedrive -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Out-File -append $env:temp\dataTest5.txt, Get-ChildItem -Path $env:programfiles -erroraction silentlycontinue | Out-File -append $env:temp\dataTest5.txt, Get-ChildItem -Path \""${env:ProgramFiles(x86)}\"" -erroraction silentlycontinue | Out-File -append $env:temp\dataTest5.txt, $UsersFolder = \""$env:homedrive\Users\\"", foreach ($directory in Get-ChildItem -Path $UsersFolder -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) , {, foreach ($secondarydirectory in $folderarray),  {Get-ChildItem -Path \""$UsersFolder/$directory/$secondarydirectory\"" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Out-File -append $env:temp\dataTest5.txt}, }, cat $env:temp\dataTest5.txt}
